%% 3.1.11 Package Management — sequence (layered)
%% Actor > UI > Controller > Service > Repository > Database

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (/packages)
    participant PC as Controller (PackageController)
    participant PS as Service (PackageService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository Package)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Open Package Management
    UI->>PC: GET /api/Package/Search
    PC->>PS: SearchPackageAsync
    PS->>Repo: Query packages
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    PS-->>PC: list
    PC-->>UI: 200 — table or cards

    Actor->>UI: Add New Package — form + Draft/Publish toggle
    UI->>PC: POST /api/Package/Create (PackageCreateDto)
    PC->>PS: CreatePackageAsync
    PS->>Repo: Insert Package row
    Repo->>DB: INSERT
    PS-->>PC: OK
    PC-->>UI: 200 — if Published, mobile catalog can GET Active

    Note over UI,DB: BR11 — nếu sửa giá bản ghi đã có đơn: tạo Package mới (version) thay vì UPDATE giá tại chỗ — cần implement trong PackageService.

    opt Publish flow
        UI->>PC: PUT /api/Package/Update/{id} status Publish
        PC->>PS: UpdatePackageAsync
        PS->>Repo: UPDATE
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE
    end
